  "title": "M&E coordinator",
  "description": "<p>Job Description</p><p>•\tReview and study M&E drawings and coordinate relevant trade works with the Consultants and Sub-Con to resolve any technical or site issues.</p><p>•\tEnsure M&E works are complied to specifications and drawings.</p><p>•\tUpdate Project Manager on site problems</p><p>•\tSupervise and monitor the work progress on site.</p><p>•\tTo arrange and attend inspection or meeting with clients or contractors</p><p>•\tCoordinate with Sub-con and ensure work are carried out and complete on schedule.</p><p>Requirements</p><p>•\tExperience in HDB residential projects</p><p>•\tFamiliar with Singapore building construction environment</p><p>•\tAble to work independently and in a team.</p><p>•\tDegree or Diploma in Mechanical or Electrical Engineering or relevant disciplines from recognised institutions.</p><p>•\tMinimum 3-5 years of relevant working experience in HDB or private residential projects.</p>",
